<!-- Setup & Run -->

ï¸- Install JSON Server
-npm install -g json-server

ï¸-Run JSON Server
-json-server --watch db.json --port 3000

The API will now be available at:

<!-- http://localhost:3000/songs -->

- Open in Browser

Just open index.html in your browser.

<!-- Usage -->

Enter a search term (song title / artist) â†’ click Search.

Use Filter Results to narrow down by artist name.

Click â–¶ Play to listen to a preview.

